### BoardBuddies User API Collection
### User 도메인 관련 API 요청들

### Create a user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "john",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "nickname": "Johnny"
}

### Get user by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1

### Get all users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users

### Update user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "johnny",
  "email": "johnny@example.com",
  "nickname": "J"
}

### Delete user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1

### Search by username
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/search?username=john

### Search by email
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/search?email=john@example.com

### Search bad request: both params (validation test)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/search?username=john&email=john@example.com
